channel.description:
Since my previous 'About me' section was boring as all Hell, said nothing about me and probably drove people away ("Who's this weirdo emphasizing the fact he wants to make videos? Fuck that") I'm going to stop being a lazy-ass weirdo and use BBC Code!

I'm Acnologia, sure that's not really my real name but duuude, this is the internet. Besides, I think Acnologia is a cool name, no? I'm also a wannabe voice actor.


One of my friends regularly sings and everytime I'm with him he starts screaming and yelling. He goes on about it in public, and even in trains. Being around him is very fun and I thought he sounded amazing. So he got me into it.
channel.title: Acnologia
